[{"id": "c0cd697d-20e7-4500-89f6-a0c3368121c8", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "USER: Hi. i just installed this writing studio? what's next?\nASSISTANT: Hey! Welcome to Lagoon.\n\nYou've got two demo characters ready to go \u2014 Hermione Granger and Nathan Young. They're fully configured, so you can jump straight into a conversation and see how everything feels before you build your own.\n\n**Quick start:**\n1. Pick a character from the dropdown\n2. Hit the chat button\n3. Start typing\n\nThat'll give you a feel for the pacing, the writing tools (Fork, Nudge, Edit in Place), and how context/memory behaves.\n\n**If you want to explore deeper:**\n- Check out a character's config \u2014 see how the system prompt, world context, and anchors are set up\n- Try the Style Overseer panel to tweak response quality rules\n\nWhat are you looking to write? A specific story, or just poking around to see what this thing can do?", "embedding": [-0.015027639456093311, -0.08080237358808517, 0.04815608263015747, 0.023209938779473305, -0.03102225624024868, -0.03618766367435455, -0.010510637424886227, 0.003795880125835538, 0.023823333904147148, 0.0007052427972666919, -0.025054780766367912, -0.007376692723482847, -0.008358965627849102, -0.04772583022713661, 0.018315514549613, 0.0068721529096364975, 0.0895928367972374, -0.0897662416100502, -0.048606812953948975, -0.011705322191119194, 0.0323108471930027, -0.050817135721445084, 0.027963923290371895, -0.008339380845427513, -0.012788137421011925, 0.007002152968198061, -0.04910019040107727, -0.004966742359101772, -0.0063036116771399975, -0.06157539412379265, -0.04638568311929703, 0.02316485531628132, 0.07942473143339157, -0.0224153995513916, 0.06167436018586159, 0.10569662600755692, 0.06257940828800201, 0.02285662665963173, -0.044729165732860565, -0.07683063298463821, -0.07192838937044144, -0.054485220462083817, -0.004150887485593557, 0.10428998619318008, 0.07444155216217041, -0.09753462672233582, -0.04513147100806236, -0.03636247292160988, -0.02